_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM4OTQwNDE5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38940419?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark","html_url":"https://github.com/mkmark","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mkmark/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-07-29T09:45:26Z","updated_at":"2022-07-29T11:06:25Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"> Hello, I was trying to achieve the same using [Docker compose](https://github.com/doccano/doccano#docker-compose) with my nginx webserver and got it work by doing following:\r\n\r\nI run under python env and I have to additionally add the prefix to all urlpatterns in [`backend/config/urls.py`](https://github.com/doccano/doccano/blob/de8d24f5f8b29399d29eda288880f78c6017f937/backend/config/urls.py#L48)\r\n\r\n```python\r\n# Add 'prefix' to all urlpatterns\r\nif settings.URL_PREFIX:\r\n    urlpatterns = [path(f'{settings.URL_PREFIX}/', include(urlpatterns))]\r\n```\r\n\r\nand in `backend/config/settings/base.py` add\r\n```python\r\nURL_PREFIX = \"mysubpath\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nOtherwise, I cannot log in.\r\nNot sure if I miss anything else.\r\n\r\nreference https://stackoverflow.com/a/56639722/18672686","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/issues/comments/1199081702/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null